lors de l'appel sur dev-phone, l'appel passe bien et atteint mon appli et OpenAI (ChatGpt), mais au retour ChatGpt j'ai cette r√©ponse (message re√ßu) qui apparait dans la  LOG.

Message received from **OpenAI server**: {

issue.title: Logging the conversation to text file
issue.body:
WoW Amazing job!

FYI: I was a bit surprised that I did not have to add my Twilio SID and Auth Token - might be good to explain that you don't have to add it. 

Could you give me a hint how to log the conversation history as a text file?

comment.body: hey! This is out of the scope of the work the maintainers have taken on here. There's options to do this and I believe in your ability to figure it out üòä
